    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/0380b3c69b3947b59601807af027743f.poster.avif?t=1743420669\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/0380b3c69b3947b59601807af027743f.webm?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/0380b3c69b3947b59601807af027743f.mp4?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>快来加入《Skye Tales》与友善小龙斯凯尔一起，飞跃莺歌燕舞又五彩斑斓的布林山谷。这个世界等不及有你的加入，快来享受惬意探索的解谜乐趣吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/44cb3b26b598b7183433de5ff9a2850c.poster.avif?t=1743420669\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/44cb3b26b598b7183433de5ff9a2850c.webm?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/44cb3b26b598b7183433de5ff9a2850c.mp4?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 通过破解轻松休闲的谜题，帮助山谷中的邻居们举办节日活动、开办一场音乐会以及扬帆起航</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/d8c693ce18c5421c840e37b9c238a644.poster.avif?t=1743420669\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/d8c693ce18c5421c840e37b9c238a644.webm?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/d8c693ce18c5421c840e37b9c238a644.mp4?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 上能飞至直抵云霄的树冠、下可潜入深不见底的矿井，从艾薇郡的田园牧歌到轻语脊的温暖沙海，探索四座风格迥异的山谷</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/3ef003a2eaf9ce829e7b23e02783eb5e.poster.avif?t=1743420669\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/3ef003a2eaf9ce829e7b23e02783eb5e.webm?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/3ef003a2eaf9ce829e7b23e02783eb5e.mp4?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 放慢脚步，在缤纷绚丽的魔法乐器与活灵活现的玩具的陪伴下，度过一段休闲时光</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/1ccbfca81d8fb264e9c7fc4d670b6493.poster.avif?t=1743420669\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/1ccbfca81d8fb264e9c7fc4d670b6493.webm?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/1ccbfca81d8fb264e9c7fc4d670b6493.mp4?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 紧跟时尚潮流，为斯凯尔的衣橱增添赏心悦目的华丽服装</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/0a2f1d1c6bd04fc2860776bdddb657a1.poster.avif?t=1743420669\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/0a2f1d1c6bd04fc2860776bdddb657a1.webm?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2138300/extras/0a2f1d1c6bd04fc2860776bdddb657a1.mp4?t=1743420669\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可视筛选以及其他辅助功能将帮助你随心所欲畅享《Skye Tales》</li></ul><br>欢天喜地的欢闹蜂、呵欠连天的蘑哞牛还有生性顽皮的水豹都已经迫不及待想与你见面！坐下来、深呼吸，让自己放松一下。趣味横生的世界期待你的到来！",
